document_data.name: Mamood's
document_data.source: [[City of Delights| City of Delights (Gem of Zakhara)]]
document_data.mainbody: '''Mamood's''' was a large tent located in [[Huzuz]] in [[1367 DR]].{{AQ-time}}
document_data.Location: Mamood's could be found in the [[Pilgrims' District]] of the City of Delights.
document_data.Inhabitants: Mamood's was owned and operated by [[Mamood]]. He offered the tent as a place to sleep for pilgrim's visiting the city for a mere one [[cp|bit]] per night. Several mercenaries stood guard to allow his guests to sleep soundly.
